snippet.title: Master Leaf Blower announcement (early gameplay) Crazy Simulator Of Leaf Blower  #masterleafblower
snippet.description:
steam wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2937290/Master_Leaf_Blower/
Master Leaf Blower is a physics-based arcade game with a comic book twist. Become a leaf-blowing hero and save the city! Navigate unique districts, tackle fun challenges, and test your skills in this crazy simulator.
www.buffa.software
music:  chiptuned-rock-music by bertsz
